    dc:title "A review of the Canthyporus exilis group, with the description of two new species (Coleoptera: Dytiscidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238996>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238992>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238993>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238994> ;
